race.comment: VAREJAO (6) has placed three of five around this circuit and is drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley. Should be right there when the judge calls a halt. ZOUSTROLOGY (7) wasn't too far away in town on debut and will have derived a stack of benefit from that day at the races. Makes plenty of appeal. RUSTENBURG (1) has just run into one better in both career outings and is a must for the multiples. LYNEHAM (9) returns from a lay-off. Fitter for a recent trial at Eagle Farm. Raced just once last campaign and finished sixth at Doomben over 1200m. In the mix fresh. SOLAR SURFER (11) resumed from a spell last start and did well to finish third over 1000m at this track. Fitter and can figure in the finish.
